# Custom Objects Inventory

This page documents active custom BigQuery tables and views (those queried at least once in the past 180 days) created specifically for Irestore4, separate from the standard SourceMedium data models.

**Last Updated (snapshot_at):** `2026-02-04 00:46:30 UTC`  
**Data Source:** Auto-generated from `sm_metadata.dim_tenant_custom_objects`. Only objects with at least 1 query in the past 180 days are included.
</Info>
